Jamaica Ave., north side, between 241st and 242nd Streets.  If locating in 1909 it would be Jericho Turnpike, north side, west of Queens Road.  This view shows a home demolished in April 1925.  Mrs. Hoagland owned it in 1873.  It was in the B.T. Kissan estate in 1896.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
